headline: MDU to Issue $200M in Shares to Fund Acquisition and Other Purposes
summary: MDU taps a $200M equity raise to support investments and reduce leverage, balancing growth with dilution effects.

headline: Mizuho Sees Atmos Energy’s (ATO) Strengths Well-Reflected in the Market
summary: Atmos Energy Corporation (NYSE:ATO) is included among the 14 Best US Stocks to Buy for Long Term. On December 2, Mizuho analyst Gabriel Moreen boosted the price target on Atmos Energy Corporation (NYSE:ATO) to $180 from $170 and maintained a Neutral rating on the stock.
